I downloaded Reach and searched the Economy Channel and the word Rural to find information to discuss with rural community members.  There was one article under Rural.  There was nothing under the Economy regarding tariffs.  Is there a way to add or suggest articles on specific topics, such as the impact of past Trump Tariffs on agriculture?

Hi <@1281612937957740558> you can go to Channels & Roles and choose Engage with your Online Communities, which will open https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1250550849998946417 and you can share your idea with the team.
